Job Description
Ali & Sons Co. LLC urgently requires the following for its After Sales Division in Abu Dhabi/ Al Ain.
- Team Leader - Mechanical
- Customer Care Supervisor
- Warranty Supervisor
- Service Advisor
- Team Leader - Painting
- Parts Advisor
- Auto Electrician
- Auto Painter
- New Car Storekeeper (w/ UAE DL)
- Auto Mechanic
- Auto Denter
- Receptionist
- Road Tester/ QC
- Wheel Alignment Technician
- Drivers
For the above positions, the candidates should have a Degree/ Diploma in Mechanical/ Automobile Engineering/ a related discipline, with minimum 3 years GCC experience in any leading car dealership in a similar position.Apply Instructions for This Job
